metadata.name: FAITH in HOPE
metadata.description:
We all believe in good, evil but did you believe in hope!

The strongest faith, women's faith in hope!

Faith in your man!
Faith of youth to create a strong marriage
Faith in your child with the hope of being a better man
Faith in love because it's steadfast 
Faith in life after death, in God.

This work is a bow to all women and our mothers!
For hope, for faith in us!
